### 🧪 Upload a file via relay using multipart/form-data
# Must set Authorization manually or via environment injection in REST Client extension

POST https://chatgpt-team.pages.dev/v1/files
Authorization: Bearer {{OPENAI_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----OpenAIRelay

------OpenAIRelay
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="purpose"

assistants
------OpenAIRelay
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="logo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./tools/logo.jpg
------OpenAIRelay--
